org.qubitpi.athena.application

Class AbstractBinderFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • application.org.qubitpi.athena.AbstractBinderFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BinderFactory

    public abstract class AbstractBinderFactory
extends Object
implements BinderFactory
    AbstractBinderFactory implements standard buildBinder functionality.

    It is left to individual projects to subclass, providing FileStore and MetaStore classes, etc.
